===Etymology 2===
From ''[[castle]]''/

====Pronunciation====
* {{IPA|/ˈkɑːsəlɪŋ/}}

====Noun====
{{en-noun|-}}

# {{chess}} A move in which the [[king]] moves two squares towards a [[rook]], and the rook moves to the other side of the king; the [[action]] of the verb ''to [[castle]]''.

